propel.core.collections.buffers

Class CircularBuffer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.buffers.CircularBuffer<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, IBuffer<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SharedBuffer

    public class CircularBuffer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IBuffer<T>
    A type-aware circular buffer of limited size. This collection does not allow nulls to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new CircularBuffer<String>(){}; -OR- new CircularBuffer<String>(String.class);
